content: Just another day at the Mar-A-Lago caddyshack… “Can you believe it, he asked me if I thought Kim Jong-un had a bigger putter than he did.” “Wha’d ya say?” “I told him that of all the people that I had caddied for, he definitely had the biggest putter.” “Don’t you mostly caddy for the ladies?” “Well yeah, but I didn’t tell him that.”
